data.description: **VA Assumable loan available to another VA entitlement loan buyer! Current rate of the loan is 5.125%**  This gorgeous well maintained 5 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in the very sought after rural part of Plant City sits on 1.17 acres of land with a 2 horse stall barn and above ground pool is looking for its new lucky homeowners. This completely updated home has so much to offer with endless possibilities. The metal roof is from 2012, A/C is 2022, 2016 water heater. As you drive up to the home, you will first see the awesome large yard with a the semi-circular driveway with two separate gates to enter and/or exit the property.When you walk in the open concept is breathtaking as you see the living room, dining room,  updated kitchen and family room not to mention the wood burning fireplace.The bedrooms are a split floor plan concept with 3 bedrooms on one side with the master bedroom and the 2 other bedrooms on the other side of the home. The large kitchen has stone counter tops with plenty of cabinet space and a large bar top good for entertaining or just eating your everyday meals. There is a large game room in the back before you enter the enclosed back patio. As you walk out in the backyard you will notice no backyard neighbors, a two stall horse barn, small wood deck, detached garage, above ground pool, and chicken coop which is all completely fenced in. The opportunities are endless for what this home and yard has to offer! Don’t miss your opportunity today to grab this home before someone else does!
